milestones.description: Kapil Dev's 175 is the highest individual score in ODIs, surpassing Glenn Turner's 171
Kapil Dev has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (100) in an innings in ODIs, going past David Gower's 96
Syed Kirmani and Kapil Dev's 126-run partnership is the highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 63 between Hadlee and Gary Troup
This is the highest match aggregate (501) involving teams India & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Kapil Dev has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (6) in ODIs for IND, going past Yashpal Sharma's 4
Peter Rawson has become the top wicket-taker for ZIM in ODIs with 8 wickets, going past Fletcher's 6
Kapil Dev's 175 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for IND), surpassing Srikkanth's 95
Kapil Dev has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (37) for IND, going past Vengsarkar
Iain Butchart has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran
Andy Pycroft has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Robin Brown's 2
Dave Houghton has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Dave Houghton's 1
Kevin Curran has conceded the most runs in an innings (65) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran's record of 57
Kapil Dev has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (100) in an innings in ODIs for IND, going past Srikkanth's 58
Syed Kirmani and Kapil Dev's 126-run partnership is IND's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 60 between Srinivas Venkataraghavan and Syed Abid Ali
Kevin Curran and Peter Rawson's 41-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Peter Rawson and Iain Butchart
